latestPosts.caption:
The B I G - 3 O 
Happy Birthdayy Pops 🤍

We’ve been through enough to write a book, chaotic chapters, wholesome ones, and a few that make zero sense (just like us) 

You’ve always shown up. Always stayed. 
Your patience is gold. 
Your humor? Top-tier nonsense (the best kind).
And your heart has room for all but thank you for giving me the biggest room. 

So today, I just want to say thank you —
For holding space, for sticking around, for loving me in my most unlovable moments.
I love you endlessly, and I’m so damn lucky to say that you are my biggest frustration. 

Now go cause chaos. It’s your day!
